snippet.textDisplay: Gotta chime in bc I have not cared to watch Zac Efron since my babysitting days back in early 2000s but this has turned me over. So impressed with how well rounded and grounded he seems. From finding out that he loves the outdoors and recharges in nature to keeping his left hands on his leg entire time and his answers. He is so much more than the frat boy persona and am glad to have watched this. As always, Sean -- you are amazing and so respectful. Now off to go watch any and all outdoors ZE stuff. Who knew he had a show? Thank you, Sean. 🌈🌈
